\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5452685 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16151623\charrsid11272464 Oh roughly, oh I should say about - three to four years between us. Possibly a little longer the girl, Lillian. Yes. Lillian.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15953395 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16151623\charrsid11272464 Do you remember how old your father was when you were born?
