\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15953395 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16151623\charrsid11272464 What }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3610829\charrsid11272464 brought your father up from Dev}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
