 up here and I think that's why he thought he'd leave the - you know, leave the - the - sea and come up - heard of this and bought this small business up in Salisbu}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3610829\charrsid11272464 r}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16151623\charrsid11272464 y Road you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15953395 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16151623\charrsid11272464 How did he meet your mother, do you know?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5452685 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16151623\charrsid11272464 He used to - he used to do quite a little bit of writing, I ought to read that to you -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15953395 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16151623\charrsid11272464 Writing?
