Well, yes, they - yes, I mean even now I've got no crave - I'd as soon have a cup of tea anytime as - yes. I mean I go out to a dinner, anything like that perhaps - well like our Dunstable Road old b
oys, they still have a yearly dinner you know, it's a real slap up do that is, oh yes, you want to come over and take - instead of that one night. Yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15953395 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16151623\charrsid11272464 Did your mother make any medicines for the family?
