Oh Lor' I don't know, didn't never buy it, rented it. Yes, oh I couldn't tell you. I don't - well father really took that on, those twenty-seven acres, we were - he was in the baking then you see, this is back -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15953395 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16151623\charrsid11272464 Before the war?
