\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15953395 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16151623\charrsid11272464 Did father employ anybody to help on that?
