ed an egg then. Yes. We never had an egg that day. No, no. No, I used to love mushrooms like - they're very nice. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15953395 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16151623\charrsid11272464 Do you ever remember mother going without so that you could have more?
