\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15953395 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16151623\charrsid11272464 How about what you had to eat, was mother strict that you had to have everything that was going or did you have to eat it up?
