\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15953395 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16151623\charrsid11272464 Did you call them Mr and Mrs.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5452685 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16151623\charrsid11272464 Mr Simpkins it was yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15953395 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16151623\charrsid11272464 You'd call them Mr and Mrs Simpkins?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5452685 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16151623\charrsid11272464 Yes, oh yes, we used to then, yes, but not for long then it was soon George - George and Maude you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15953395 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16151623\charrsid11272464 You called them by their Christian names?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5452685 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16151623\charrsid11272464 Yes, Christian names, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15953395 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16151623\charrsid11272464 Not mum and dad?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5452685 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16151623\charrsid11272464 No, no, no, just their Christian names. Oh that was the - the sister. Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15953395 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16151623\charrsid11272464 But what about her parents?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5452685 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16151623\charrsid11272464 The parents, well - well don't know wha
t we used to call them really, it wasn't necessary to with ordinary just talking away you see, yes, I mean -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15953395 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16151623\charrsid11272464 Can you remember before your marriage if you called them Mr and Mrs?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5452685 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16151623\charrsid11272464 Oh Mr and Mrs then, oh pray yes, oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15953395 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16151623\charrsid11272464 And afterwards do you remember, you called her gran just now when you were talking about her?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5452685 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16151623\charrsid11272464 Yes, usually did call her gran, yes, well of course she was getting on - I was then -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15953395 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16151623\charrsid11272464 When you had children sort of thing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5452685 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16151623\charrsid11272464 Yes, I was going to say that - with this ga
rdening lark she'd often say well of course, she said - as soon as I've finished with the garden I shall be finished. Always used to say that you know. And now there you are, now - now how old - how old was she the last time she done the garden? There you
 
are, have a guess. She done that garden perfect. Ninety-three. She died when she was ninety-five, yes. Ninety three and - then afterwards we had to take it on you know and - and umpteen times the wife says, well - how grandma could stick out here, the hou
rs she used to I shall never know, see. I must go and have a sit down. And that's how we used to be you see. Oh I'll - I'll go in and make a cup of tea, see, and - yes, that's how we used to be. Yes, nin}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid10505068\charrsid11272464 e}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16151623\charrsid11272464 ty-three - last time she done the garden. Cor.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15953395 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16151623\charrsid11272464 You didn't drink did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5452685 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16151623\charrsid11272464 No, no, nothing to speak of.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15953395 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16151623\charrsid11272464 Did her father drink?
