\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15953395 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16151623\charrsid11272464 How did your mother think of her, can you remember?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5452685 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16151623\charrsid11272464 
Oh yes, she liked her, yes, oh yes, she liked her, no they got on real well really. I think it was more or less sort of a case you know - perhaps mother'd look at - looking out the window and see me 
chatting with her perhaps as she was going back to work like you know. And - sort of - oh - led on more or less and - 'course I mean you see - we used to serve them, we used to serve them then when they was in - Salisbury Road you see. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15953395 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16151623\charrsid11272464 Did you ever write to each other?
