 write then two or three times during the week you see. Oh yes, that's how we used to like that, yes. Was
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15953395 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16151623\charrsid11272464 Was she your first girlfriend or had you had others?
