Well I think so, yes. There was - there was - several of us you know all quite real pals and that together but I wouldn't say that - you know, we used to all like each other, there was a chap there Aubrey Wright, now he was a darned good vio
linist you see, and sometimes he'd come in on a Sunday night and - and - with the singing you see and - playing his old violin and that you know and - well and then it was like tea and sandwiches and all the rest of it and - and of course he was more or l
ess sort of one of the gang that used to be playing outside you know, in the evening. But - look out, here comes the copper, and off we used to dash.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15953395 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16151623\charrsid11272464 Did anybody ever try to discourage you from going out with your wife?
