ures, whichever was on, like if there was anything decent on like really and - oh we was all much the same you know, more like - we always liked the old - fashioned music and that, and of course we went out - used to go out like to the Dunstable Road - Ol
d Boys dinner you see and - we have gone out for dinners and we used to always dance and that you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15953395 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16151623\charrsid11272464 Go out for walks?
