\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15953395 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16151623\charrsid11272464 You were allowed to go by yourselves were you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5452685 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16151623\charrsid11272464 Oh yes, yes. Yes. No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15953395 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16151623\charrsid11272464 You carried on going out in groups of friends as well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5452685 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16151623\charrsid11272464 
Yes, we used to do that, yes, one of our - yes, on a Wednesday, see when we shut our businesses up Wednesdays, we'd always - sort of interlock with each other as regards the riding, you see, perhaps the 
wife'd say, oh well we were over so and so - a fortnight ago, they'd better ride with us this week you see and so on you see and then - we used to perhaps - assemble at their different places like there was one there in - in - in - a big butcher he was, I
 used to call in there perhaps just before they'd shut the shop on a Wed - on a Monday night see. Well you ride with us this week will you. Yes, righto Bert, OK, yes righto, that's it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15953395 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16151623\charrsid11272464 Riding what?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5452685 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16151623\charrsid11272464 In the cars. We'd go perhaps two, three, someti
mes four cars. We have been five cars, gone out and I'll tell you one of our trips we used to run up to Northampton Market - just have a look round the market there on a Wednesday and then come across to - Bedford - and there was some nice - tennis courts
 
there, we used to have a game of tennis there on these courts, that's all built up now I know where - where we used to play, and then used to come down into - you know, the Granada there and have a high tea, and then come on home you see, then - when we g
o
t home it - it just depended - oh, they was all there, well they'd all come in our place and have coffee and biscuits and that for the evening you see. Then the next Wednesday - oh well, what about it, shall we go up - let's have a - let's go up to Gunner
s
bury, see, well sometimes we used to go down to Gunnersbury and - perhaps Gunnersbury park and have a game miniature golf. And then when we used to do that then - we used to - cut straight away up through - Hammersmith Broad way and straight up to London,
 have a high tea at Flemings in Oxford Street see, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15953395 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16151623\charrsid11272464 You had a good time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5452685 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16151623\charrsid11272464 
Oh yes, and that's what I said to - I said to some of the people - I was only talking about it on Sunday as a matter of fact, they said well of course you can't do that 
today, you - you can't put the car anywhere you see, we used to just run up there, into Oxford Street. Just turn off Oxford Street - from one of the squares there you see, put the cars there, four, five cars it would be, lock 'em up and walk on round into
 Oxford Street and - go to Flemings and - have a high tea.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15953395 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16151623\charrsid11272464 Before you were married did you ever have a holiday together?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5452685 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16151623\charrsid11272464 No. No, no, never.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15953395 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16151623\charrsid11272464 Would that have been allowed to you think or not?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5452685 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16151623\charrsid11272464 Well I don't know, well I doubt it really. No, we never did, no, never thought of it at all. They might do these days of course.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15953395 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16151623\charrsid11272464 Do you remember a moment when you decided to get married?
