Oh yes, yes, I asked them, yes, yes, yes, yes. And I asked mother and that as well, I mean I was telling mother about it you see. No, she said, I shouldn't make no objection because she's such a nice person you see, mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15953395 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16151623\charrsid11272464 What about her parents?
